<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挠了挠头：“你认识这头猪？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 悟空敲打着铁门，“起床了，懒猪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒从床上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 他看了看四周，“是谁在叫我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈，悟空。” 八戒假笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你来这个世界就是为了笑我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来找你的。” 悟空转向史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒怎么会在监狱里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个小偷。” 史密斯侦探回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不可能！” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒一直在努力向善，而且他知道偷东西是不好的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他偷吃了很多食物。” 史密斯侦探说，“但是他没有付钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，好吧。” 悟空点了点头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个我相信，现在你可以放了他，我们要回到师父身边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探摇了摇头：“我不能让八戒离开监狱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说什么？” 悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他犯了法。” 史密斯侦探双臂交叉，“我不能让他离开。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西去哪儿了？” 玛拉对杰克和特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个朋友在杰克家，他们用手机玩儿游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望罗西没事儿。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔没说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道罗西那天晚上去做火箭女孩儿了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但从那以后，他们就没有罗西的消息了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，玛拉的手机响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看这条大新闻！” 玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天和火箭女孩儿打斗的那头大猪从监狱里逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只会说话的猴子帮了他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？” 特勒尔弯下身子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，这里还有视频！” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉点开了视频，他们看到美罗城监狱的一面墙炸开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大猪从里面跳出来，后面跟着一只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子挥着铁棒，打中了一辆警车，然后他们跳上一朵云，飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克张大了嘴巴：“那只猴子太酷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西盯着丑陋的妖怪：“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是黑雨大王。” 他回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴能请到你这样强大的女神仙来做客。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很惊讶：“你为什么会觉得我是女神仙？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你有强大的力量。” 黑雨大王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点了点头：“没错，但我不是女神仙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抓住了唐僧。” 黑雨大王接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我愿意和你一起分享他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧是谁？” 罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且你说的‘分享’是什么意思？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧是一个了不起的僧人。” 黑雨大王说着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脸上露出了大大的笑容，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃了他，就可以长生不老！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真邪恶！” 罗西说，“我现在就去放了他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向门口跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你敢！” 黑雨大王大喊，他跳到罗西的面前挡住了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西握紧了拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！强风暴雨吹进山洞，把罗西吹倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西在空中翻滚，四处碰撞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风把她吹出山洞，吹向了天边的太阳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她掉在了一个灌木丛中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！山洞的门关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>